These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, june
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, argentine
House: modern, townhouse
1. the modern house is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##8
2. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the japanese##5
3. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | tea     | coffee      |
| Birthday          | june | march    |
| Nationality         | argentine   | japanese |
| House   | modern  | townhouse      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, june
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, woodworking
There 2 different types of food: kiwi, plum
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: disaster, musical
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person eating kiwi##5
3. the person eating plum is not to the right of the person eating kiwi##8
4. the person watching disaster movies is not the person who's hobby is woodworking##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Birthday    | august        | june    |
| Hobby       | filmmaking         | woodworking |
| Food         | plum | kiwi   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster               | musical  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, tiparillo
There are 2 different favourite colors: lilac, grey
2 different games are played: poker, chess
2 different pets are kept: cat, ferret
1. the person playing poker is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing chess is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
3. the person who likes lilac is somewhere to the left of the tiparillo-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Cigar   | pall-mall       | tiparillo |
| Color   | lilac       | grey    |
| Game   | poker | chess |
| Pet           | cat        | ferret   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
