2 different games are played: scrabble, whist
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, cauliflower
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, tram
1. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the right of the person playing whist##5
2. the victorian house is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| House         | ranch-style | victorian  |
| Game           | whist  | scrabble |
| Food   | cauliflower | broccoli   |
| Transport     | tram   | airplane |

